Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:44.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}毀滅終結的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:54.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}無情的宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:01:07.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你獨自聽到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:20.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我做了一個遙遠的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該放棄什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:25.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該決定什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:26.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}我算什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:30.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}早已經決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:31.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}有沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}對著神質問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我並非獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:45.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你一直在身邊 對我伸出這雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}沒什麼好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:02:00.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}即便化為怪物也要完成願望
